Complexity Analysis
Time Complexity

Each iteration eliminates half of the search space.

n → n/2 → n/4 → n/8 ...

Therefore:

O(log n)
Space Complexity

Only a few variables are used.

O(1)
Key Takeaway

For a Rotated Sorted Array:

Find mid.
Determine which half is sorted.
Check if the target lies inside that sorted half.
Search the appropriate half.
